<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Brazil Health Connect</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/reveal.js/dist/reveal.css">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/reveal.js/dist/reveal.js"></script>

  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .reveal {
      color: #111827;
    }

    h1, h2 {
      color: #2563EB;
    }

    .logo {
      position: absolute;
      top: 20px;
      right: 20px;
      width: 80px;
    }

    .hex {
      width: 120px;
      height: 70px;
      background: #FACC15;
      opacity: 0.2;
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 30px;
      left: 30px;
      clip-path: polygon(
        25% 0%, 75% 0%, 
        100% 50%, 75% 100%, 
        25% 100%, 0% 50%
      );
    }

    .triangle {
      width: 0;
      height: 0;
      border-left: 60px solid transparent;
      border-right: 60px solid transparent;
      border-top: 100px solid #FACC15;
      opacity: 0.2;
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 20px;
      left: 20px;
    }

    .line {
      width: 100%;
      height: 2px;
      background: #2563EB;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .box {
      border: 1px solid #FACC15;
      padding: 10px;
      margin: 10px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

  </style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="reveal">
<div class="slides">

<!-- SLIDE 1 -->
<section>
<img src="logo.png" class="logo">
<div class="hex"></div>

<h1>Brazil Health Connect</h1>

<p>
Hi everyone, Professor.<br>
My name is Arthur Vinicius.<br><br>

I chose this brand because when I came to the United States to study, I saw how expensive healthcare is here...<br><br>

Brazil Health Connect connects Brazilians living around the world with Brazilian doctors – more affordable, easier, and more human.
</p>
</section>

<!-- SLIDE 2 -->
<section>
<img src="logo.png" class="logo">

<h2>The 4Ps</h2>
<div class="line"></div>

<div class="box">
<b>Product</b><br>
Telehealth consultations with Brazilian doctors
</div>

<div class="box">
<b>Price</b><br>
$30 – $50 per consultation
</div>

<div class="box">
<b>Place</b><br>
100% digital – anywhere
</div>

<div class="box">
<b>Promotion</b><br>
Instagram and TikTok
</div>

</section>

<!-- SLIDE 3 -->
<section>
<img src="logo.png" class="logo">
<div class="triangle"></div>

<h2>Competitive Advantage</h2>

<p>
Lower Price<br>
Language & Culture<br><br>

Customer Excellence<br>
Operational Excellence<br>
Product Excellence<br>
Locational Excellence
</p>
</section>

<!-- SLIDE 4 -->
<section>
<img src="logo.png" class="logo">
<div class="hex" style="background:#2563EB;"></div>

<h2>STP</h2>

<ul>
<li>Brazilian students (18–35)</li>
<li>Reachable via social media</li>
<li>Responsive audience</li>
</ul>

<p><b>“Affordable Brazilian healthcare anywhere.”</b></p>
</section>

<!-- SLIDE 5 -->
<section>
<h2>Thank you!</h2>

<p>
Brazil Health Connect is a bridge...<br><br>

Any questions?<br><br>

Arthur Vinicius
</p>
</section>

</div>
</div>

<script>
Reveal.initialize();
</script>

</body>
</html>
